Frank Dane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Dane 0 Frank Dane was a British actor of the silent era.Dane was born Frank Hughbert Thomas Crust on 7 June 1885 in Deal, Kent. He died in 1957 at age 71 in Chichester, Sussex. Frank_Dane was a_British_actor of the_silent_era.Dane was_born Frank_Hughbert_Thomas_Crust on 7_June_1885 in Deal , Kent .
